{"tid":721643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【優品360°傳主板上市】　老闆：點解你咁快知","createTime":"2018-06-28T22:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T06:45:37.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bac14fc3b2834ca6493fa62dea2c592558e3055f","tid":721643,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T22:26:24.000Z","msg":"連鎖零食店「優品360&deg;」將於短期內遞交上市申請，擬於主板掛牌，集資約2億元。優品360&deg;老闆林子峰接受本報查詢時表示：「點解你會咁快知嘅？我依家唔方便講。」<br />\n<br />\n零食店的經營模式多是「薄利多銷」，市場預期優品360&deg;毛利率偏低。以阿信屋為例，零售業務截至去年10月底止中期收入達8.6億元，毛利有3.53億元，經營溢利僅得199.2萬元，經營溢利率為0.23%，即每100元僅賺得兩毫子"},{"pid":"504f66d82a7b2bae839b35b78892dc4d25bdd556","tid":721643,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T22:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180628/large/1530178651_da67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180628%2Flarge%2F1530178651_da67.jpg&h=871f554f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4beee67e9594d9c956c46110c193147831baf165","tid":721643,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"天氣熱行經759都會買到嘢飲<br />\n鳩撚360真係未幫襯過，歐洲零食無乜興趣"},{"pid":"1309594552dc67f66faaebd3b1b78817e5f833ea","tid":721643,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":42,"score":-41,"quote":{"pid":"4beee67e9594d9c956c46110c193147831baf165","tid":721643,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"天氣熱行經759都會買到嘢飲<br />\n鳩撚360真係未幫襯過，歐洲零食無乜興趣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T23:00:24.000Z","msg":"無冰櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe2540745d3ca89436bdc85597f825f48f11400","tid":721643,"uid":51932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T23:03:28.000Z","msg":"聽講係佢度做嘢要簽保密協議，啲阿姐會知啲咩機密嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97aa34841fd7bb82949e62f74c89fe82e14c2f94","tid